Kalidou Koulibaly just signed a transfer agreement with Chelsea, moving from Napoli, and he will soon join the London squad in Las Vegas.
While many supporters applaud Koulibaly’s transfer, others object to the idea of Chelsea combining two overage players at the back (Thiago Silva and Koulibaly).
Below are comments made by fans in response to a post about Silva and Koulibaly that was made by ESPN UK.
