Despite the fact that age may not be on Silva and Koulibaly’s sides, both have established themselves as some of the top players in the game.
Chelsea has been linked with other defenders such as Presnel Kimpembe and Nathan Ake from PSG and Man City respectively and they hope to have the signature of one of them.
The Blues had a very successful season last year, and they will be striving for an even better one this coming year.


